msgstr "<b>Dans l'app Inventaire :</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Locate the customer's last invoice.</b>"
msgstr "<b>Trouvez la dernière facture du client.</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Login as:</b>"
msgstr "<b>Se connecter en tant que :</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manage your package types:</b> Define all\n"
"                        the types of packages you handle (e.g., pallets, "
"boxes). These will be used\n"
"                        to create <b>Storage Categories</b>, which help you "
"optimize warehouse\n"
"                        space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Gérez vos types de colis :</b> définissez tous\n"
"                    les types de colis que vous manipulez (par ex. palettes, "
"boîtes). Ils seront utilisés\n"
"                    pour créer des <b>catégories de stockage</b>, qui vous "
"aident à optimiser l’espace\n"
"                    de l’entrepôt."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manutention Report:</b> Provides details on completed transfers and\n"
"                            the number of packages created by type and the "
"quantity of products\n"
"                            delivered."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rapport de manutention :</b> fournit des détails sur les transferts "
"terminés et\n"
"                        le nombre de colis créés par type ainsi que la "
"quantité de produits\n"
"                        livrés."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Note:</b> Storage data is updated daily, so it's not live. Be sure to\n"
"                            select a date that is not today."
msgstr ""
"<b>Remarque :</b> les données de stockage sont mises à jour quotidiennement, "
"elles ne sont donc pas en temps réel.\n"
"                        Assurez-vous de sélectionner une date différente "
"d’aujourd’hui."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Odoo will automatically duplicate</b> the previous invoice,\n"
"                                    using the correct start date (based on "
"your defined invoice\n"
"                                    period) but setting <b>all\n"
"                                        quantity lines to\n"
"                                        zero</b>. This prevents accidental "
"overbilling and allows\n"
"                                    you to input the current period's "
"quantities accurately."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odoo dupliquera automatiquement</b> la facture précédente,\n"
"                                en utilisant la bonne date de début (basée "
"sur votre période de facturation définie), mais en mettant <b>toutes\n"
"                                    les lignes de quantité à\n"
"                                    zéro</b>. Cela évite toute "
"surfacturation accidentelle et vous permet\n"
"                                de saisir avec précision les quantités de la "
"période en cours."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Open the CRM app</b> and create a new opportunity."
msgstr "<b>Ouvrez l'app CRM</b> et créez une nouvelle opportunité."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Password:</b> portal"
msgstr "<b>Mot de passe :</b> portal"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Picking Optimization:</b> Optimize picking with different methods like "
"<b>Batch\n"
"                            Picking, Wave Picking,</b> and <b>Cluster "
"Picking</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Optimisation du transfert :</b> optimisez le transfert avec différentes "
"méthodes telles que\n"
"                        <b>batch picking, wave picking,</b> et <b>cluster "
"picking</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Putaway Rules:</b> Customize how products are stored based on your own\n"
"                            rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Règles de mise en stock :</b> personnalisez la manière dont les produits "
"sont stockés selon\n"
"                        vos propres règles."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Quality Report:</b> Gives information on the number of quality checks\n"
"                            performed."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rapport qualité :</b> donne des informations sur le nombre de contrôles "
"qualité\n"
"                        effectués."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Reserved Quantity:</b> The amount of stock that has already been "
"allocated for\n"
"                    a scheduled shipment."
msgstr ""
"<b>Quantité réservée :</b> la quantité de stock déjà allouée à une livraison "
"planifiée."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Set up location-based fees:</b> In the configuration, you can define\n"
"                        different <b>Fee Rates</b> and link them to specific "
"storage locations. This\n"
"                        lets you apply different prices to various types of "
"storage, such as\n"
"                        refrigerated or high-bay areas. This granular "
"control allows for automated\n"
"                        and accurate invoicing based on the number of "
"pallets per fee rate."
msgstr ""
"<b>Configurez des frais basés sur l’emplacement :</b> dans la configuration, "
"vous pouvez définir\n"
"                    différents <b>tarifs</b> et les lier à des emplacements "
"de stockage spécifiques. Cela\n"
"                    vous permet d’appliquer différents prix à divers types "
"de stockage, comme\n"
"                    les zones réfrigérées ou en hauteur. Ce niveau de détail "
"permet une\n"
"                    facturation automatisée et précise basée sur le nombre "
"de palettes par tarif."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Shipping Connector:</b> Connect with various carriers directly within\n"
"                            Odoo."
msgstr ""
"<b>Connecteur d’expédition :</b> connectez-vous à différents transporteurs "
"directement dans\n"
"                        Odoo."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Storage Report:</b> Shows the amount of packages stored per day,\n"
"                            broken down by fee rate."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rapport de stockage :</b> affiche le nombre de colis stockés par jour,\n"
"                        ventilé par tarif."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>User:</b> portal@portal.com"
msgstr "<b>Utilisateur :</b> portal@portal.com"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the invoice."
msgstr "<b>Validez</b> la facture."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the quotation to finalize the sales order."
msgstr "<b>Validez</b> le devis pour finaliser la commande client."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the transfer."
msgstr "<b>Validez</b> le transfert."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> to finalize the order."
msgstr "<b>Validez</b> afin de finaliser la commande."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.ir_ui_view_2473
msgid ""
"<br/>Leverage advanced 3PL automation and real-time transparency for "
"unparalleled efficiency and competitive advantage.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>Exploitez l’automatisation avancée 3PL et la transparence en temps réel "
"pour une efficacité inégalée et un avantage concurrentiel.<br/><br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<em>Example:  A category named \"5 Std Pal\" can be configured to hold\n"
"                        five standard pallets.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>Exemple : une catégorie nommée \"5 Std Pal\" peut être configurée pour "
"contenir\n"
"                    cinq palettes standard.</em>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<em>Example: A client who had 150 pallets at €0.30/day and 55 pallets at\n"
"                        €0.45/day in August.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>Exemple : un client ayant 150 palettes à 0,30 €/jour et 55 palettes à\n"
"                    0,45 €/jour en août.</em>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Barcode App</b>:</font> Streamlines "
"warehouse floor operations by enabling\n"
"                    fast and accurate scanning of pallets, locations, and "
"stock movements."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Code-barres</b> :</font> rationalise les "
"opérations en entrepôt en permettant\n"
"                un scan rapide et précis des palettes, emplacements et "
"mouvements de stock."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM App</b>:</font> Tracks leads and "
"opportunities efficiently, helping\n"
"                    logistics companies follow up on prospects and manage "
"long-term customer relationships."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM</b> :</font> suit efficacement les "
"pistes et opportunités, aidant\n"
"                les entreprises logistiques à suivre les prospects et gérer "
"des relations clients à long terme."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Documents App</b>:</font> Centralizes "
"contracts, delivery notes, and\n"
"                    transport documentation in a searchable digital space."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Documents</b> :</font> centralise les "
"contrats, bons de livraison et\n"
"                documents de transport dans un espace numérique consultable."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventory App</b>:</font> Enables precise "
"stock management across multiple\n"
"                    warehouses and clients, ensuring full tracking of "
"inbound, outbound, and internal movements."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventaire</b> :</font> permet une gestion "
"précise des stocks sur plusieurs\n"
"                entrepôts et clients, assurant un suivi complet des "
"mouvements entrants, sortants et internes."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Invoicing App</b>:</font> Automates "
"billing calculations based on storage\n"
"                    duration, volume, and handling services, with support "
"for custom pricing per client."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Facturation</b> :</font> automatise les "
"calculs de facturation basés sur la durée de stockage,\n"
"                le volume et les services de manutention, avec prise en "
"charge de tarifs personnalisés par client."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Sales App</b>:</font> Generates "
"professional quotations and sales orders for\n"
"                    storage, transport, and value-added logistics services."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Ventes</b> :</font> génère des devis "
"professionnels et des commandes client pour\n"
"                les services de stockage, transport et logistique à valeur "
"ajoutée."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Subscriptions App</b>:</font> Manages "
"recurring billing for long-term\n"
"                    storage services with customizable plans."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Abonnements</b> :</font> gère la "
"facturation récurrente pour les services de stockage à long terme\n"
"                avec des formules personnalisables."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Website &amp; Portal</b>:</font> Provides "
"clients with a self-service portal\n"
"                    for real-time access to stock levels, service requests, "
"and downloadable documents."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Site Web &amp; Portail</b> :</font> "
"fournit aux clients un portail en libre-service\n"
"                pour un accès en temps réel aux niveaux de stock, aux "
"demandes de service et aux documents téléchargeables."

