#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Storage Report pulls data from <b>Inventory/Reporting/Stock History</b>."
msgstr ""
"Le rapport de stockage extrait les données de <b>Inventaire/Rapports/"
"Historique des stocks</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The app streamlines the invoicing process for these\n"
"            agreements. Additionally, you can access reports on occupancy "
"and dates to help\n"
"            anticipate and manage your storage capacity."
msgstr ""
"L’app simplifie le processus de facturation pour ces\n"
"        contrats. De plus, vous pouvez accéder à des rapports sur "
"l’occupation et les dates afin de vous aider\n"
"        à anticiper et gérer votre capacité de stockage."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The barcode app can be installed as a\n"
"                        standalone application on devices. This means people "
"can use it without\n"
"                        having access to the rest of the database."
msgstr ""
"L’app Code-barres peut être installée comme\n"
"                    application autonome sur les appareils. Cela signifie "
"que les utilisateurs peuvent l’utiliser sans\n"
"                    avoir accès au reste de la base de données."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "The customer reminders."
msgstr "Les rappels clients."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The customer will then receive an email with instructions to create their "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Le client recevra ensuite un email contenant les instructions pour créer son "
"compte."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The dashboard provides all the necessary information,\n"
"            including storage occupancy, completed transfers, created "
"packages, and performed\n"
"            quality checks. You just need to manually adjust the quantities "
"on your invoices using\n"
"            this data."
msgstr ""
"Le tableau de bord fournit toutes les informations nécessaires,\n"
"        y compris l’occupation du stockage, les transferts terminés, les "
"colis créés et les contrôles\n"
"        qualité effectués. Vous devez simplement ajuster manuellement les "
"quantités sur vos factures à l’aide\n"
"        de ces données."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "The dashboard provides the following reports:"
msgstr "Le tableau de bord fournit les rapports suivants :"

